web_snippets: Andy Manson is a luthier who has been hand-crafting guitars for over four decades. He has also made mandolins and multi-necked instruments.
For the English guitar maker, see Andy Manson (luthier). Andrew Bruce Manson (23 March 1936 – 22 December 2009) is a former Australian politician and orator.
